Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.67,0:27:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The field of consciousness itself then\Nhas only it doesn't do anything. It just
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.24,0:27:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is\Nit registers everything that happens
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.91,0:27:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,for everything that happens. So it's\Nlike a giant electro electrostatic
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.67,0:27:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,field.\NEvery thought, everything that happens
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.27,0:27:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in the universe, every human being,\Nevery living thing
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.24,0:27:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,uh radiates energy. And this energy\Nradiation, every thought that you have,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.15,0:27:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,every movement, every decision,\Nit has a consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.48,0:27:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And the consequence is registered within\Nthe field of consciousness. The field of
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.08,0:28:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness is not a flat fl\Nelectromagnetic
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.03,0:28:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,electrostatic speaker but it is\Neverywhere present at all times
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.84,0:28:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,everywhere equally present.\NAll that happens all that's ever said
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.20,0:28:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,thought felt all that's ever existed\Nis automatically recorded in this field
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.72,0:28:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,forever.\NEvery thought you've ever had is
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.84,0:28:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,recorded forever.\NScripture says every hair on your head
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.84,0:28:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,should be counted. That is a fact.\NIt's usually held up as a threat. Every
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.24,0:28:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,hair I'm hear is going to be counted.\NEvery kind thought you have is also
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.88,0:28:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,thought recorded.\NHappily, positive thoughts are so much
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.96,0:28:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,more powerful than negative thoughts.\NFrankly, you can have negative thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.88,0:29:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,all day long. Have one happy, loving\Nthought, it wipes it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.12,0:29:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Positive thoughts are so infinitely more\Npowerful than negative thoughts. But
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.03,0:29:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,negative thoughts by their sheer\Nmultiplicity have an effect in the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.60,0:29:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,world.\NWhen I first saw kinesiology, it was Dr.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.72,0:29:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,John Diamond and\NNew York City. It was one of those iffy
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.03,0:29:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of things and I went because people\Nof you know pretty good awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.48,0:29:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,recommended it. So when I went to see uh\NJohn Diamond, he was demonstrating
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.52,0:29:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,kinesiology the way it's used in\Nclinical medicine, holistic health and
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.36,0:29:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,holistic medicine.\NYou know, you hold a turnup next to your
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.32,0:29:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,solar plexus and it makes your arm go\Nweak. I'm sure they come here for a week
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.88,0:29:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,at Colorado.\NMy grandmother was from Ireland.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.15,0:30:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Colorado's birthday turnips on.\NSo the only difference was the audience
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.00,0:30:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,saw it as a local phenomena. They saw it\Nas the turnup now makes your arm go
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.36,0:30:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,weak.\NSo we found that in the presence of that
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.60,0:30:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,which is positive your arm goes strong.\NIn the presence of that which is false
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.55,0:30:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,or negative your arm goes weak. That\Nwhich supports life makes the arm go
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.00,0:30:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,strong. That which is unimicable to\Nlife. False being one of them makes the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.12,0:30:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,arm go weak. And this is an impersonal\Nreaction of the field of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.39,0:30:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,itself. It's impersonal. It doesn't care\Nwhat you think at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.32,0:30:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So Susie and I have done it so many\Ntimes, millions of times, hundred for
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.27,0:30:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,this current book that we're putting\Nout. We did 7,000 calibrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.36,0:30:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,7,000 times the world couldn't care\Nless. The physi the arm just goes weak
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.64,0:31:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in the presence of falsehood and it goes\Nstrong in the presence of that which is
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.15,0:31:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,positive. So you might say it's sort of\Na quality of life. It's almost like
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.03,0:31:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,protoplasm. It's impersonal like a\Nprotoplasmic response.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.32,0:31:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Protoplasm knows like an amoeba knows\Nthat which is good for it. The amoeba
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.48,0:31:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,goes opens towards that which is\Nlifegiving and it retracts and closes up
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.76,0:31:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and withdraws from that which is\Nlife-threatening to it. It's an
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.60,0:31:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,automatic consequence. It's not\Npersonal. First difficulty people
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.20,0:31:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,usually have is they think it's\Npersonal. However, we get the same
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.44,0:31:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly the same answers if we verbalize\Nthem or we don't verbalize them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.15,0:31:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, when it's a very important\Ncalibration, I'll say what I'm holding
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.51,0:31:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in mind calibrates over 200, 300, 340,\N420, 2020.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.72,0:31:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do one. We won't tell audience\Nwhat it is. I'm holding in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.72,0:31:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates over 420, 421. Okay. Now, I'm\Ngoing to hold something else in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.79,0:32:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm holding mine, calibrates over\N422.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.03,0:32:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm holding mine calibrates over 423.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.32,0:32:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know what I'm holding in\Nmind.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.55,0:32:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how does it happen? If if she\Ndoesn't know what I'm holding in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.55,0:32:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,how can her arm respond with yes or no?\NIt's because it's happening within the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.48,0:32:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,field of consciousness itself.\NThe thought form I'm holding interacts
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.15,0:32:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,with her electrostatic field.\NWhen she goes weak, the acupuncture
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.88,0:32:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,system is temporarily out of commission\Nand that's the kinesiologic response.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.20,0:32:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The field of consciousness then\Nrecognizes truth. It goes strong in the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.91,0:32:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,presence of truth. It doesn't go weak in\Nthe presence of false. So it just
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.39,0:33:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't respond.\NTherefore, the kinesiologic response is
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.64,0:33:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,not yes versus no. It's\NTrue versus not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.91,0:33:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an important duality to trans\Ntranscend.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.84,0:33:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not yes versus no. A thing is\Neither true or not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.60,0:33:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, in reality, there is no such\Nthing as falsehood because that would be
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.79,0:33:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,non-truth and non-truth has no\Nexistence.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.32,0:33:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that which exists make your arm go\Nstrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.27,0:33:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is false and has no existence\Nhas no charge. In the presence of
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.55,0:33:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,nothingness, the arm goes weak. So it's\Nnot yes versus no.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.48,0:33:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true versus the absence of truth.\NThere is no opposite to truth. It's
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.79,0:33:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,either present or absent. We'll get to\Nthat on a slide. Like there's no
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.51,0:34:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,opposite to light.\NDarkness is merely its opposite, but
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.32,0:34:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not it is merely its absence. I'm\Nsorry. It's absence, not its absence,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.67,0:34:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,not its opposite. All right. So, we\Ntalked today about the calibrated levels
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.87,0:34:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness and this is how they\Nevolved and we calibrated them on a
