Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.84,1:29:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,from somewhere\NAnd with that was scrupulosity,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.48,1:29:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,fear of sin. The Gothic downside of\NChristianity
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.40,1:29:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,gets fixated on sin. So it isn't that\Nyou live for goodness, it's that you
