Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.36,1:29:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, like\Nand God can see this. Whoa. I must have
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.56,1:29:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,dreaded that.\NSaturday afternoon, I'd go to high
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.15,1:29:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Episcopal was very much like Catholic.\NSo, you went to confession on Saturday
