Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.23,1:30:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,4:30 after confession to God absolution.\NYou did all the rosary deals
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.40,1:30:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,until I would go to the earliest mass on\NSunday. So the shortest time for sin to
