Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.71,1:30:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,sinless spotless up to this point. It's\Nnow about 18 minutes to 7.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.63,1:30:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we round the corner,\Nthere's a 30 foot long billboard of a
