Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.71,1:31:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Lord, forgive me for the wickedness\Nof my thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.80,1:31:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Lord, forgive me for the lust of my\Nthoughts. Forgive me for Oh my god, it
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.76,1:31:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,was torture. No,\NI didn't dare tell my folks why I wasn't
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.56,1:31:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,going to go to communion that morning.\NI had to fake it. I got a spot on my
