Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.44,1:31:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was respiring. I get up to communion\Nreal.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.52,1:31:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was afraid.\NI felt like it was striking.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.96,1:31:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Went to communion with a spot on your\Nsoul. So you live in the dread of
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.88,1:31:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,religion. It was not a source of joy.\NNot like unity church. Let me tell you
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.28,1:31:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it was the downside. Yeah.\NAnyway, eventually I became
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.60,1:31:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,intellectual. Studied all the great\Nbooks of the western world. Not all good
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.04,1:32:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,ones. Aristotle Socrates. Socrates is my\Nhero. I was a little skinny ecamorph
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.96,1:32:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,with thick glasses. And I read Socrates\Nwhile other people had stick ball.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.88,1:32:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He rzled and did other disgusting\Nphysically aggressive things.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.44,1:32:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweaty and greasy. Good.\NAristotle, Socrates, they were my
