Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.88,1:32:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Socrates went to death rather than\Nviolate truth rather than violate the
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.71,1:32:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,truth of God. He accepted death when he\Ncould have chickened out and capped out
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.08,1:32:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the deal. Said rather than violate\Nwhere did he get that religion? Because
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.00,1:32:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Christianity wasn't born yet. Buddhism\Nhad gotten to Greece.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.19,1:32:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So now Socrates got it cal 540\Nunconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.36,1:33:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So he was a hero.\NAnyway, then I got into intellectualism
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.00,1:33:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,became an atheist and then I was a\Nsincere atheist for 20 years
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.76,1:33:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and I went to a Jesuit university\Nvarious things
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.52,1:33:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and uh became got straight A in\Ntheology.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.96,1:33:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,going to argue it. You better know a lot\Nabout it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.71,1:33:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,>> You have to do have a beer and argue\Ntheology,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.44,1:33:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,metaphysics. It was a wonderful life. I\Nwas an art atheist.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.67,1:33:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But then the exingencies of life. I was\Nin World War II.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.84,1:33:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And uh the thing that happened after\Nthat snowbank experience curiosity
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.23,1:33:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,curiously uh was a complete boss of fear\Nof death. Never had fear of death since.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.40,1:33:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody says that'll kill you. So I say\Nso
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.12,1:33:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean here's this mine right next to\Nthe ship ready to go off any second. We
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.04,1:34:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,got these boat hooks. The only thing\Nwe're concerned about is that this thing
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.40,1:34:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldn't hit the boat.\NThe fact they could blow up and kill you
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.15,1:34:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't even in her mind. You don't let\Nit hit the boat. You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.36,1:34:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh god.\NSo there we are. I was an atheist and uh
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.44,1:34:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually I needed to I was preoccupied\Nwith the core essence truth itself all
