Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.08,1:35:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to find what is the core and the\Nessence of truth you know Socrates was a
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.56,1:35:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,big help\Nbut there was a driveness to discover
